{"product_id":"organic-cleansing-milk-100ml","title":"Vielö Organic Cleansing Milk 100ml","description":"\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eGentle organic cleansing milk to remove make-up and dirt effortlessly. Soothes the skin, leaving it soft and hydrated.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), organic wheat germ oil (nurturing), organic rosehip seed oil (soothing) and organic extracts of chamomile (antiseptic), arnica (anti-inflammatory) and sage (antibacterial).\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into dry skin across face and neck. Rinse with lukewarm water. Use it in the morning and evening and whenever your skin needs natural cleansing. Shake before use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/Stearate*, Glycerin**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Aqua*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Lavandula Angusti- folia Flower Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelar- gonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Geraniol**\/***, Sodium Lactate*, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Limonene**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (87,1%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49092148592967,"sku":null,"price":32.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-cleansing-milk-100ml-720327.jpg?v=1739897336","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/organic-cleansing-milk-100ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}